wdi-GC.REV.XGRT.CN.def: Revenue is cash receipts from taxes, social contributions, and other revenues such as fines, fees, rent, and income from property or sales. Grants are also considered as revenue but are excluded here.
wdi-GC.REV.XGRT.CN.name: Revenue
wdi-GC.REV.XGRT.CN.source: International Monetary Fund, Government Finance Statistics Yearbook and data files.
